{"tid":1855964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"★理大何文田宿舍有懷疑個案須被隔離","createTime":"2020-02-01T11:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T11:43:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"395d5ef49cfd92ae3fad681d311bac947280c7ec","tid":1855964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"【編委報導】新hall有懷疑個案須被隔離<br />\n<br />\n本會記者日前發現何文田宿舍宿生向接待處職員表示自己需要被隔離，當時職員支吾以對，但承認有宿生需要隔離。<br />\n<br />\n最近本會記者再到何文田宿舍查詢有關事宜，其中一名舍監聲稱所有隔離個案均曾到訪武漢或湖北省一帶，但都沒有出現武漢肺炎病徵。舍堂已根據衞生署指引將所有懷疑個案呈報給校方。<br />\n<br />\n本會已電郵至舍堂生活及學生資源處查詢有關事件，校方至今未有正式書面回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAeVPvh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAeVPvh.jpg&h=74e90f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/photos/a.479538842112752/2761240990609181/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpusupresscom%2Fphotos%2Fa.479538842112752%2F2761240990609181%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=8109d8bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/photos/a.479538842112752/2761240990609181/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"6aae1686e5afbfbc8acd9b99d316b0cda4ad8e0c","tid":1855964,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a660277384ff12c7e9bc7fa73a57864325a7319","tid":1855964,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,